<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Infinitely" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Infinitely,</orth> boundlessly, endlessly: <cit><quote>to whom I am so i. bound,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 5.135" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 135</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I love thee i.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.3.105" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 3, 105</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>promise you i.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.5.132" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 5, 132</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>so i. endeared,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 1.2.233" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 2, 233</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to whose kindnesses I am most i. tied,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 23</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>